```
My prefix is "3!"

3!help                      Lists available commands
3!kick [@user] [reason]     Kicks the mentioned user
3!ban [@user] [reason]      Bans the mentioned user
3!mute [@user]              Mutes the mentioned user
3!unmute [@user]            Unmutes the mentioned user
```
